# 06 - Risk Assessment

## Purpose

This section evaluates risks by combining assets, threats, and vulnerabilities into risk scenarios.

## File

- Risk-Assessment.xlsx

## Methodology

Risk Score = Likelihood x Impact

Risk ratings are categorized as Low, Medium, High, or Critical.

## Skills Demonstrated

- Risk scoring
- Likelihood and impact analysis
- Risk prioritization
- ISO 27001 risk assessment methodology
